'''''Return of the Reaper''''' is the 17th album from German [[heavy metal music|heavy metal]] band [[Grave Digger (band)|Grave Digger]], which was released on 11 July 2014 via [[Napalm Records]]. This is the final album to feature H.P. Katzenburg on keyboards.<ref>{{cite web |author= |title=GRAVE DIGGER: 'Return Of The Reaper' Track Listing Revealed|url=http://www.blabbermouth.net/news/grave-digger-return-of-the-reaper-track-listing-revealed/ |publisher=[[Blabbermouth.net]] |accessdate=April 23, 2014}}</ref>

