==Album Information==

The album cover was created by Gyula Havancsák of Hjules Illustration and Design, who has been responsible for all of the band's artworks since 2005's ''[[The Last Supper (Grave Digger album)|The Last Supper]]''.

When given a description about the album, Chris Boltendahl cites the album stylistically reminiscent of ''[[Heavy Metal Breakdown]]'', ''[[Witch Hunter (album)|Witch Hunter]]'' and ''[[The Reaper (Grave Digger album)|The Reaper]]''.

==Personnel==
* [[Chris Boltendahl]] - Vocals
* [[Axel Ritt]] - Guitars
* [[Jens Becker]] - Bass
* [[Stefan Arnold]] - Drums
* [[H.P. Katzenburg]] - Keyboards

==Production==
* Gyula Havancsák - Cover Art

